---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="HRC Case Study — RelayLaunch"
  description="How RelayLaunch replaced $342/month in disconnected tools with $51/month in unified infrastructure for the Holistic Rejuvenation Center at the JW Marriott Turnberry, Miami."
>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ HERO -->
  <section class="section hero">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/case-studies" class="back-link">← Case Studies</a>
      <div class="cs-meta">
        <span class="badge badge-green">Wellness / Hospitality</span>
        <span class="cs-location">JW Marriott Turnberry · Aventura, FL</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="hero-headline">
        $342/month in disconnected tools<br />
        replaced with <span class="text-green">$51/month</span> in unified infrastructure.
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        The Holistic Rejuvenation Center — a luxury spa and wellness brand embedded in the
        JW Marriott Turnberry — was paying for five separate platforms that didn't talk to each
        other. RelayLaunch replaced the entire stack with one connected system. Annual savings: $3,492.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ HEADLINE STATS -->
  <section class="stats-bar">
    <div class="container stats-grid">
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-number green">$342 → $51</div>
        <div class="stat-label">monthly infrastructure cost</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-number">$3,492</div>
        <div class="stat-label">saved every year</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-number">11</div>
        <div class="stat-label">automation workflows running 24/7</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-number">$50k+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">market value delivered at $0 upfront</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ CLIENT -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container two-col">
      <div>
        <span class="section-eyebrow">The Client</span>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 36px);">Holistic Rejuvenation Center / mé Spa &amp; Wellness</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-muted); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 16px;">
          Elaine Kroytor runs a luxury holistic wellness practice embedded in the JW Marriott
          Turnberry in Aventura, Florida — a five-star resort property. Her business spans
          personalized spa services, corporate wellness programs, and a growing membership community.
        </p>
        <p style="color: var(--color-muted); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 16px;">
          Elaine is exceptional at her craft. But like most service business owners, she found
          herself spending significant time managing platforms instead of serving clients —
          patching together tools that weren't built to work together.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card before-card">
        <p class="section-eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">Before RelayLaunch</p>
        <table class="rl-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Tool</th>
              <th>Monthly Cost</th>
              <th>Problem</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>ClickFunnels</td>
              <td>$127/mo</td>
              <td>Disconnected from website</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Squarespace</td>
              <td>$65/mo</td>
              <td>No automation, slow, generic</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Manual social posting</td>
              <td>~$80/mo time cost</td>
              <td>2+ hours/week, inconsistent</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Manual follow-ups</td>
              <td>~$70/mo time cost</td>
              <td>Leads falling through</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Total</strong></td>
              <td><strong>$342+/mo</strong></td>
              <td>Zero automation</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ THE PROBLEM -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-surface);">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">The Problem</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Five tools. Zero automation. Hours lost every week.</h2>
      <div class="problem-grid">
        <div class="problem-item">
          <div class="problem-icon">💸</div>
          <h3>Tool Sprawl</h3>
          <p>ClickFunnels + Squarespace + standalone email + manual social + spreadsheets — none connected, all requiring separate logins and manual data entry between them.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-item">
          <div class="problem-icon">🕐</div>
          <h3>Time Drain</h3>
          <p>Follow-ups, social posts, booking confirmations, review requests — all done manually. Estimated 8–12 hours per week in work that should be automated.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-item">
          <div class="problem-icon">👁️</div>
          <h3>Invisible Online</h3>
          <p>The existing website was template-based, slow, and not optimized for search. A luxury brand at a five-star resort deserved better digital presence than a $65/month template.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-item">
          <div class="problem-icon">📉</div>
          <h3>Missed Revenue</h3>
          <p>No lead nurturing, no automated booking follow-ups, no email sequences. Potential clients who expressed interest were falling through the cracks with no system to catch them.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ THE SOLUTION -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">The Solution</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">One connected system.<br />Everything automated.</h2>
      <p class="section-sub" style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
        RelayLaunch replaced the entire stack with unified infrastructure: custom website,
        11 automation workflows, email sequences, social scheduling, and a Slack dashboard
        that briefs Elaine every morning — all for $51/month in total infrastructure costs.
      </p>

      <div class="deliverables-grid">
        <div class="card deliverable-card">
          <div class="del-icon">🌐</div>
          <h3>15-Page Custom Website</h3>
          <p>Built in Astro 6 — mobile-first, SEO-optimized, deployed on Cloudflare Pages at $0/month hosting. Replaces Squarespace entirely.</p>
          <div class="del-value">Market value: $3,000–$8,000</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card deliverable-card">
          <div class="del-icon">⚡</div>
          <h3>11 Automation Workflows</h3>
          <p>n8n-powered workflows running 24/7: booking confirmations, follow-ups, review requests, lead nurturing, social publishing, and internal alerts.</p>
          <div class="del-value">Market value: $3,500–$10,500</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card deliverable-card">
          <div class="del-icon">✉️</div>
          <h3>5 Email Sequences</h3>
          <p>Welcome series, booking follow-up, membership nurture, re-engagement, and corporate wellness outreach — all triggered automatically.</p>
          <div class="del-value">Market value: $500–$1,500</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card deliverable-card">
          <div class="del-icon">📱</div>
          <h3>30 Days of Social Content</h3>
          <p>Scheduled across 4 platforms (Instagram, Facebook, LinkedIn, Google Business). Consistent brand presence without the 8+ hours/week manual work.</p>
          <div class="del-value">Market value: $500–$1,500/mo</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card deliverable-card">
          <div class="del-icon">📊</div>
          <h3>Slack Automated Dashboard</h3>
          <p>Daily briefings with bookings, leads, social engagement, and alerts. Every morning, the business reports to Elaine — not the other way around.</p>
          <div class="del-value">Market value: $500–$1,500</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card deliverable-card">
          <div class="del-icon">👥</div>
          <h3>Membership Platform</h3>
          <p>"Join the Tribe" — free and paid membership tiers with automated onboarding, exclusive content access, and community management.</p>
          <div class="del-value">Market value: $1,500–$3,500</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card deliverable-card">
          <div class="del-icon">🏢</div>
          <h3>Corporate Wellness Sub-Site</h3>
          <p>A dedicated section for corporate wellness packages — 3 service tiers, intake form, and automated follow-up. A new revenue channel, activated.</p>
          <div class="del-value">Market value: $1,000–$2,500</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card deliverable-card">
          <div class="del-icon">✍️</div>
          <h3>8 SEO Blog Posts</h3>
          <p>Long-form, keyword-targeted content establishing authority in the Miami wellness space and driving organic search traffic.</p>
          <div class="del-value">Market value: $800–$1,500</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card deliverable-card">
          <div class="del-icon">🔄</div>
          <h3>Full Platform Migration</h3>
          <p>Clean migration from ClickFunnels and Squarespace — all content, assets, and existing workflows moved without disruption to the business.</p>
          <div class="del-value">Market value: $1,500–$3,000</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ RESULTS -->
  <section class="section results-section">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">The Results</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">$3,492 back every year.<br />From day one.</h2>

      <div class="results-grid">
        <div>
          <table class="rl-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>What Changed</th>
                <th>Before</th>
                <th>After</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>Monthly infrastructure cost</td>
                <td class="red-val">$342+/mo</td>
                <td class="green-val">$51/mo</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Annual savings</td>
                <td class="red-val">—</td>
                <td class="green-val">$3,492/yr</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Booking follow-ups</td>
                <td class="red-val">Manual, inconsistent</td>
                <td class="green-val">Automated, same-day</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Social posting</td>
                <td class="red-val">2+ hrs/week manual</td>
                <td class="green-val">Scheduled, 4 platforms</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Lead nurturing</td>
                <td class="red-val">Zero — leads fell through</td>
                <td class="green-val">5 automated sequences</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Website hosting</td>
                <td class="red-val">$65/mo (Squarespace)</td>
                <td class="green-val">$0/mo (Cloudflare Pages)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Business visibility</td>
                <td class="red-val">Generic template, slow</td>
                <td class="green-val">SEO-optimized, fast, ranked</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Morning briefing</td>
                <td class="red-val">5 logins, 30 min</td>
                <td class="green-val">1 Slack dashboard, 2 min</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div class="card total-value-card">
            <p class="section-eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">Total Value Delivered</p>
            <div class="value-range">$17,000 — $52,000</div>
            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-muted); margin-top: 8px;">
              Estimated market value of all deliverables, based on standard agency rates.
            </p>
            <div class="value-breakdown">
              <div class="vb-row">
                <span>Custom website (15 pages)</span>
                <span>$3,000–$8,000</span>
              </div>
              <div class="vb-row">
                <span>11 automation workflows</span>
                <span>$3,500–$10,500</span>
              </div>
              <div class="vb-row">
                <span>Email sequences (5)</span>
                <span>$500–$1,500</span>
              </div>
              <div class="vb-row">
                <span>Social content (30 days)</span>
                <span>$500–$1,500</span>
              </div>
              <div class="vb-row">
                <span>Slack dashboard</span>
                <span>$500–$1,500</span>
              </div>
              <div class="vb-row">
                <span>Membership platform</span>
                <span>$1,500–$3,500</span>
              </div>
              <div class="vb-row">
                <span>Corporate sub-site</span>
                <span>$1,000–$2,500</span>
              </div>
              <div class="vb-row">
                <span>SEO blog posts (8)</span>
                <span>$800–$1,500</span>
              </div>
              <div class="vb-row">
                <span>Platform migration</span>
                <span>$1,500–$3,000</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="value-note">Delivered at $0 upfront as a portfolio build.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ CTA -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-surface);">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">
      <h2 class="section-title">This is what RelayLaunch builds.</h2>
      <p class="section-sub" style="margin: 16px auto 32px; max-width: 520px;">
        The same unified infrastructure approach, applied to your business. Start with a Signal audit
        or jump straight into a build — we'll figure out the right fit together.
      </p>
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Start Your Build →</a>
        <a href="/services" class="btn-secondary">See All Packages</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .hero { padding-top: 80px; }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }
  .back-link:hover { color: var(--color-text); text-decoration: none; }

  .cs-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cs-location {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  .hero-headline {
    font-size: clamp(30px, 4.5vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    max-width: 800px;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .text-green { color: var(--color-green); }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    max-width: 640px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Stats bar */
  .stats-bar {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    padding: 36px 0;
  }
  .stats-grid {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .stat { text-align: center; flex: 1; padding: 16px; }
  .stat-divider { width: 1px; height: 48px; background: var(--color-border); flex-shrink: 0; }
  .stat-number.green { color: var(--color-green); }

  /* Two col */
  .two-col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .before-card { padding: 24px; }

  /* Problem grid */
  .problem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }
  .problem-item {
    padding: 24px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }
  .problem-icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .problem-item h3 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .problem-item p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.65; }

  /* Deliverables grid */
  .deliverables-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .deliverable-card { padding: 24px; }
  .del-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .deliverable-card h3 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .deliverable-card p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .del-value {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-green);
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    padding-top: 12px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  /* Results */
  .results-section { background: var(--color-surface); }
  .results-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 380px;
    gap: 40px;
    margin-top: 40px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .red-val { color: #f85149; font-size: 13px; }
  .green-val { color: var(--color-green); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; }

  .total-value-card { padding: 24px; }
  .value-range {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .value-breakdown {
    margin-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-top: 16px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .vb-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }
  .value-note {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-green);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 16px;
    padding-top: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .results-grid, .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .stats-grid { flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .stat-divider { display: none; }
    .stat { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); flex: 0 0 50%; }
    .stat:last-child, .stat:nth-last-child(2):nth-child(odd) { border-bottom: none; }
  }
</style>
